els-attack-on-iran-could-accelerate-their-nuclear-program/0000018f-15db-d361-a3ef-57fbfb320000</guid></item><item><title>“我在基布兹长大。相信我，中国不是共产主义国家”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/i-grew-up-on-a-kibbutz-believe-me-china-is-not-communist/0000018f-159a-da70-a7bf-7d9bf76d0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名想要在中国传播“犹太之光”的以色列律师，以及一名收集了大量日本发夹的网络技术工作者</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 14:54:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/i-grew-up-on-a-kibbutz-believe-me-china-is-not-communist/0000018f-159a-da70-a7bf-7d9bf76d0000</guid></item><item><title>创纪录的热浪袭击以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/record-breaking-heat-wave-hits-israel/0000018f-1548-dc39-a9cf-b5ce79ab0000</link><description>以色列气象局执行主任阿米尔·吉瓦蒂博士说，像这样的热浪是全球变暖趋势的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 13:25:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/record-breaking-heat-wave-hits-israel/0000018f-1548-dc39-a9cf-b5ce79ab0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登和其他 17 名世界领导人呼吁立即释放加沙哈马斯扣押的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/biden-17-other-world-leaders-call-for-immediate-release-of-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza/0000018f-155c-d361-a3ef-57fd397b0001</link><description>一名美国高级官员否认了有关以色列是达成人质释放协议的主要障碍的指控，并将责任完全归咎于哈马斯。信中呼吁哈马斯释放人质，以实现加沙立即长期停火</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 13:17:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-25/ty-article/.premium/biden-17-other-world-leaders-call-for-immediate-release-of-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza/0000018f-155c-d361-a3ef-57fd397b0001</guid></item><item><title>这位以色列艺术家对法国大师的改造令巴黎印象深刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-artist-whose-twist-on-french-masters-is-impressing-paris/0000018f-10ca-d97f-a